{"tid":2433930,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"營救理大案再有其中19名被告排期開審 分別於23年4月及23年9月開審","createTime":"2021-03-05T07:55:09.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-05T13:29:11.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"98d6039cd060433fb84a44b74ff7342bb4d79a22","tid":2433930,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:55:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F14163&d=eRHmMhW6fCYgFX7Mu85bUo26uSpwD1fkwqqc2qDkc5E%3D&h=f5b9c01d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/14163</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第三庭 <br />\n#區域法院案件<br />\n#高勁修區域法院首席法官 <br />\n#1118理大 #提訊<br />\n<br />\nD1: 陳<br />\nD2: 盧<br />\nD3: 禤 <br />\nD4: 鄺<br />\nD5: 黃<br />\nD6: 李 <br />\nD7: 柯<br />\nD8: 陳 <br />\nD9: 温<br />\nD10: 譚<br />\nD11: 謝 <br />\nD12: 吳 <br />\nD13: 黃<br />\nD14: 馬 <br />\nD15: 梁<br />\nD16: 陸<br />\nD17: 鄭<br />\nD18: 林 <br />\nD19: 李<br />\n<br />\n控罪：<br />\n（1）暴動（指向D1-19）<br />\n<br />\n（2）管有物品意圖摧毀財產（指向D5）<br />\n<br />\n（3）未能在規定下出示身分證明文件（指向D5）<br />\n<br />\n（4）管有適合作非法用途的工具（指向D9）<br />\n<br />\n（5）有意圖而導致他人身體受嚴重傷害（指向D9）<br />\n<br />\n（6）-（18）在身處非法集結時使用蒙面物品<br />\n（分別指向D1,2,3,5,6,7,10,11,12,14,15,16,17）<br />\n<br />\n（19）無牌管有無線電通訊器具<br />\n（指向D8）<br />\n================<br />\n<br />\n控方表示已收齊辯方回覆，並已於3月3日去信知會法庭，案件將分拆成2組。<br />\n<br />\n第一組<br />\n（D2,D4,D6,D7,D9,D12,D14,D15,D17,D18,D19）<br />\n此組別將不爭議證物連鎖性及不爭議錄影片段真確性<br />\n<br />\nPTR日期：2023年3月10日1430<br />\nTrial日期：2023年4月11日至5月23日（共30日審期，中文審訊）<br />\n<br />\n第二組<br />\n（D1,D3,D5,D8,D10,D11,D13,D16）<br />\n<br />\nPTR日期：2023年8月11日1430<br />\nTrial日期：2023年9月11日至10月24日（共30日審期，中文審訊）<br />\n<br />\n地點：灣仔區域法院<br />\n<br />\n19名被告均不認罪❗️<br />\n<br />\n案件當中涉及特別職務警察，故控方將為部分證人申請保密令。<br />\n<br />\nD4申請修改報到日期，獲批✅<br />\nD5申請修改報到地點，獲批✅<br />\nD8申請修改報到時間及地點，獲批✅<br />\nD15申請修改報到時間，獲批✅<br />\nD18申請修改報到時間，獲批✅<br />\n<br />\n其他被告以原有條件繼續保釋外出候審，直至審期"},{"pid":"21b8cc1e7e32a2ef57aa64cdb8ecf79eec80b56e","tid":2433930,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f04d51f1b86a2aca7f5793dcaa667869c2c69ca","tid":2433930,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"23年 年尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f1e593ff02d279cbf5cc67a806bb6ea0082814","tid":2433930,"uid":270307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7ab2bb020bd531325c2a17649b5c3d8c4a495a","tid":2433930,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:57:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bb14f2cd9df794e41a3b40685264cffd87f2bc3","tid":2433930,"uid":284932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T07:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c167e285aef1608f5d990ede0737ddd2cd02d945","tid":2433930,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-05T08:04:07.000